headline: Is Mohawk Industries Stock Underperforming the Dow?
summary: Mohawk Industries has significantly underperformed the Dow over the past year, but notably outperformed in recent months, and analysts remain optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: 3 Consumer Stocks with Open Questions
summary: Most consumer discretionary businesses succeed or fail based on the broader economy. This volatility leads to big swings in stock prices that have worked in their favor recently - over the past six months, the industry has returned 19.6% and beat the S&P 500 by 4.8 percentage points.
